text: Chakwal is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Chakwal may also refer to: *Chakwal District, a district situated in Pakistan. *Chakwal Tehsil, an administrative unit of Chakwal district. *Chakwal railway station, a railway station in Pakistan, ==See also== *Chakwal-Khushab Road, a road track linking the Khushab with Chakwal. * *
title: Chakwal (disambiguation)
